1. Ja *dobijam* paket sutra. (I am receiving a package tomorrow.)
2. Oni *dobiju* nagradu za najbolji film. (They receive an award for the best movie.)
3. Ti ćeš *dobiti* kaznu ako pređeš preko crvenog svetla. (You will get a fine if you cross the red light.)
4. Oni su *dobili* otkaz zbog lošeg ponašanja. (They got fired because of bad behavior.)
5. Ja sam *dobila* odgovor na svoj mejl. (I received an answer to my email.)
6. Da li si *dobio* moju poruku? (Did you get my message?)
7. Oni će *dobiti* priliku da putuju u inostranstvo. (They will get a chance to travel abroad.)
8. Nemoj da *dobiješ* groznicu zbog hladnoće. (Don't catch a cold because of the cold weather.)
9. Oni *dobijaju* pomoć od svojih prijatelja. (They are getting help from their friends.)
10. Kada ćeš *dobiti* rezultate testa? (When will you receive the test results?)

(Note: The word "dobiju" is highlighted with a star (*) in each sentence where it appears.)